{"tid":282737,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"點解IT人到30歲就會被炒 但工程師唔會","createTime":"2017-06-13T15:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T05:58:20.000Z","uid":75893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c1d7501e61d21d6cf78d4570d34e8d04a151b2","tid":282737,"uid":75893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:18:31.000Z","msg":"如果人到30歲轉數會慢，咁IT佬同engine佬都會慢啦，點解得IT會炒?<br />\n因為IT要成日學新野，人到30歲學野慢就被炒?<br />\n但好多新programming language/framework你有個底，會快pickup好多<br />\n有30歲經驗咁豐富，理應pickup得好快，慢在邊?<br />\n<br />\n點解普遍人見30-40歲既programmer會覺得佢轉數慢冇用、唔會尊重你，但見到30-40歲既engine、accountant會覺得佢好有經驗、係公司既asset，但明明engine同accountant都要計數, 係食腦既工)<br />\n<br />\n求解"},{"pid":"3f894ddb34fbbca9ba050a779a656f2511af5ccd","tid":282737,"uid":110163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"行業文化<br />\n<br />\n同香港冇野做都要扮ot既文化一樣<br />\n<br />\n無得解"},{"pid":"ae6057b107e0d879dd306eb2187cad3ac5f9e421","tid":282737,"uid":29460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"因為Engineer嘅經驗係累積<br />\nIT經驗係會過期"},{"pid":"3841297dabdf6b37475b5e215c2836c67aec1f5c","tid":282737,"uid":120051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:23:28.000Z","msg":"不可一, 不可再<br />\n向IT 説不, 向工程説得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b15b3ccd7a38e783df6897a9a49a2fde0190a0","tid":282737,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:24:05.000Z","msg":"工程師係唔會比人炒，只會比人壓價。<br />\n由三萬銀請一個變到萬五銀請兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5429969e28607acdfdf52ca8a209858f221f8d48","tid":282737,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:24:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為Engineer嘅經驗係累積<br />\nIT經驗係會過期</blockquote><br />\n就好似潮流咁<br />\n一樣野 興5年 但係5年後 有另一樣野取代左<br />\n咁你個5年既經驗就變得無用 <br />\n要學新野補返"},{"pid":"8a744968076806485b4ee395e65b4d4a4934341f","tid":2827